OL,3,CTeenager endured 'violent death' after
OL,4,Csuffering a single stab, inquest hears
OL,6,FTeenager endured a "violent death"
OL,7,Fafter suffering a single stab wound to
OL,8,Fher chest, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FChloe Watson Dransfield, 16, from
OL,11,FGomersal, died after being found with
OL,12,Fstab wounds in Kennerleigh Avenue,
OL,13,FAusthorpe on Saturday 28 March.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
