CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776082266
OL,3,CTeenager endured 'violent death' after
OL,4,Csuffering a single stab, inquest hears
OL,6,FKayla Smith, 18, of Kennerleigh
OL,7,FAvenue, Archie Rycroft, 19, of
OL,8,FMiddleton Park Road, and a 17-year-old
OL,9,Fboy who cannot be named for legal
OL,10,Freasons, have been charged with murder
OL,11,Fand are expected to stand trial at
OL,12,FLeeds Crown Court in November this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FOn Friday (April 10), an inquest into
OL,16,FChloe's death was opened at Wakefield
OL,17,FCoroner's Court.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776082266
OL,3,CTeenager endured 'violent death' after
OL,4,Csuffering a single stab, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe area coroner, Oliver Longstaff,
OL,7,Ftold the court that a post-mortem
OL,8,Fexamination found Chloe had died after
OL,9,Fsuffering a stab wound to her chest.
OL,11,FHe said said Chloe met a "violent
OL,12,Fdeath" before adjourning proceedings
OL,13,Funtil the outcome of the criminal
OL,14,Fproceedings.
OL,16,FThe court heard it was Chloe's
OL,17,Fheartbroken father Mark who formally
OL,18,Fidentified his daughter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
