CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776082266
OL,3,CTeenager endured 'violent death' after
OL,4,Csuffering a single stab, inquest hears
OL,6,FIn statements following her death,
OL,7,FChloe's family said: "My beautiful
OL,8,Fprincess Chloe. I cannot put into
OL,9,Fwords how I feel that you are not here
OL,10,Fwith me. You are my life, my world, my
OL,11,Fbest friend and I know that I am
OL,12,Fyours. I cannot live without you - I
OL,13,Fneed you.
OL,15,F"You are stunning, confident, loyal,
OL,16,Fhonest and my family-oriented
OL,17,Fprincess. When you walk into any room
OL,18,Fit lights up with your bubbly
OL,19,Fpersonality. There is so much I could
OL,20,Fsay. There's a big hole in my heart
OL,21,Fthat can never be filled.
OL,26,@oD@VOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
