FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776082266
OL,3,CTeenager endured 'violent death' after
OL,4,Csuffering a single stab, inquest hears
OL,6,F"She embraced life with such
OL,7,Fhappiness, and she had her whole
OL,8,Ffuture ahead of her. Chloe was loved
OL,9,Fby everyone who knew her, and the
OL,10,Fabsence she leaves behind is
OL,11,Fimmeasurable.
OL,13,F"We will miss her forever, she will
OL,14,Fnever be forgotten."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
